article_id:1997,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Facility Event, Divine Deception, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/791319fd0e12b1b3963ac3878e22f42c.png,message:<div>A new facility event, Divine Deception, will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1614319200"></span>!<br>This event will pit your group of adventurers against bosses of the wind element. You&#39;ll also be able to get an event-related reward facility!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a6dab872fd2d0933b606a6f97c559a71.png"></div><div>During their travels in North Grastaea, the prince and friends visit a mountain village called Paradise where a woman has been rewriting people&#39;s memories&mdash;a power seemingly granted by a sealing stone&#39;s miasma. They and several apostles begin investigating the incident, but nothing can prepare them for what they will discover...<br><br>â– Event Duration<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1614319200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1615442399"></span><br><br>Notes:<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1614146400,update_time1613526184